More likely what happened was
<br />

<br />
-spell was cast, timer was 18 sec
<br />
-by the time you put your cursor over the buff slot, more than 0.001 sec had passed, since the buff duration is rounded down to the nearest "tick" 17.9999 sec remaining showed up as 12 sec.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=653282" target=_blank>Casala</a>
