				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I simply LOVE Pyrilen Skin. Fantastic for soloing, excellent in groups against resisty mobs, for putting in to replace every third bolt to manage aggro and allow greater dps rate when needed, this was a truely inspired idea at SoE. In group settings with one tank and a single mage, think of it as a non-aggro Lure+ nuke (ie cant be resisted).
<br />

<br />
Since getting this spell, I now often only have one nuke in my nine-spell lineup, only need BoJ when there is Pyrilen Skin to use.
<br />

<br />
/cheer
