				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Best macro for pyrilen skin is this:
<br />

<br />
/target <span style="text-decoration: underline">NAME</span>
<br />
/pause 2
<br />
/target <span style="text-decoration: underline">NAME</span>
<br />
/cast <span style="text-decoration: underline">number of pyrelin skin on spell bar</span>
<br />

<br />
This is because its very easy to hit wrong target with Pyrilen Skin, thus a macro rocks.
<br />
The pause and two occassions of target are needed to make SURE it hits the correct target: I've tested this a lot.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=304331" target="_blank" class="postlink"><span style="font-weight: bold"><span style="color: red">REDORIOUS.....ARCHMAGE.....KARANA</span></span></a>
