<br />
i got this too and it pissed me off no end, so now as i always assist the tank on pulls anyway to set pet on it before casting PS, just make your macro /assist instead of /target <tank>, this works way better in range, but also means you dont need to change the macro every time you get a new tank.<br />_________________<br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Floatty Fluffycloud</span>
